\\u00c3\\u00a9s comme quantit\\u00c3\\u00a9s n\\u00c3\\u00a9gligeables, en sont exclus.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alors que ces\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"JO \\u00c3\\u00a9taient cens\\u00c3\\u00a9s \\u00c3\\u00aatre populaires\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"les parisiens\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"consid\\u00c3\\u00a9r\\u00c3\\u00a9s comme\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"quantit\\u00c3\\u00a9\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2939}, {\"ngram\": \"n\\u00c3\\u00a9gligeables\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"sont exclus\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"J\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ose \\u00c3 peine imaginer l\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099enfer pour les personnes \\u00c3 mobilit\\u00c3\\u00a9 r\\u00c3\\u00a9duite.#saccageparispic.twitter.com/XLvAZnlaEb Barriers have begun sprouting all over the place in Paris, making it difficult for wheelchair users to navigate the streets, which is again putting people off.\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3142, \"end\": 3147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.800485135826244e-20, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00c3 peine imaginer\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"pour les\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c3\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"mobilit\\u00c3\\u00a9 r\\u00c3\\u00a9duite.#saccageparispic.twitter.com/XLvAZnlaEb\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"Barriers\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"wheelchair users\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What an awful feeling to find yourself caged in your own neighbourhood,' one local resident, @EricKLein_, posted on X.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your own neighbourhood\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"X.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'While these Olympics were supposed to be popular, Parisians, considered a negligible number, were excluded.\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3432}, {\"ngram\": \"a negligible number\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hardly dare imagine hell for people with reduced mobility.'\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3507}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3518}, {\"ngram\": \"reduced mobility\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris' decision to host the Olympics was controversial with a lot of French people - given the country is already heavily in debt and the capital's finances are alarming.\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3544, \"end\": 3549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.800485135826244e-20, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3613, \"end\": 3626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3580}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3604,